room_title: Escape room "Time Travel Trouble" by Armadillo Escape Room Adventures in Houston
room_address: 417 Gentry St. Units E&F Old Town Spring, TX 77373
room_description:
You finally had a week off from work and you were planning the vacation of a lifetime! The first ever time machine is up and running and bookings are available to the public for vacation getaways. Since the opportunity presented itself, you were one of the first to eagerly sign up!
There is a warning in your tickets: it is possible that something goes terribly wrong, and you will only have 60 minutes to get back to the present time before getting stuck in the past forever! Even with the warning, you proceeded with the registration. Will you have the vacation of a lifetime or will you be stuck in a different time?
